Brent Jennings https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brent_Jennings 0 Brent Jennings (born 1951) is an American actor. He was born in Little Rock, Arkansas and is a 1969 graduate of Little Rock Central High School. He played Oakland Athletics coach Ron Washington (former manager of Texas Rangers) in 2011 film Moneyball. Brent_Jennings ( born 1951 ) is an_American_actor .
